{"tid":1755801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港零時論壇】第一次公民論壇大會","createTime":"2019-11-25T18:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T12:52:28.000Z","uid":262340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68a19776d1fb6c6dfb8bbe584c6e3bb574668ee1","tid":1755801,"uid":262340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:24:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n我地香港零時論壇嚟近將會搞第一次公民論壇大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkFHkZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkFHkZA.jpg&h=e278c2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><em>點解要搞公民論壇大會？</em></ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地要對抗林鄭政府虛假嘅「和你傾」討論會，創造翻一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">名副其實嘅</span></span></strong>「和你傾」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望香港可以好似1860年代的美國一樣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">隨時隨地</span></span></strong>就可以討論對唔同社會議題，而地點唔再限係維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>呢個論壇有咩用啊？</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比唔同年齡，唔同區嘅香港人有機會聚埋一齊，齊齊傾社會時事；<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提升香港人嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">公民意識</span></strong></span>and政治參與度；<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />互相了解and尊重<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔同<span style=\"color: green;\">政</span><span style=\"color: red;\">治</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">譜</span>嘅諗法</span></strong>，令香港變得真正多元化。正如姐姐話齋，無一個執政黨係永遠執政嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>所以無一種聲音or意見係永遠當道嘅</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>有咩要注意啊？</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得預先<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">睇多D有關主題嘅資料</span></span></strong>啊～如果唔係去到就無嘢好傾ga啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個活動係咁多位香港人自然地聚埋一齊，咁啱發現大家都有嘢傾，所以就<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">自自然然</span></span></strong>咁展開咗討論，所以係無任何and唔需要formal嘅申請書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為咗平衡在場人士嘅權益，有D<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則</span></span></strong>希望大家可以遵守<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個活動係好和理非，睇落去好似無咩作用咁<br />\n但係「無大台」要持續落去，就需要每一位香港人學識做功課（包括研究唔同文獻、案例）、學發言，而<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔係再靠代議士做嗮所有嘢</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來獨裁嘅政權最鍾意嘅就係豬</span></span></strong></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以香港人要變得更加聰明、大膽，我地先會有更多本錢and籌碼去對抗任何不公義嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用翻掛係天安門個個死人嘅說話：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">沒有調查就沒有發言權！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持，亦都希望呢個風氣可以蔓延全香港<br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"b5e61239c7147067d029bca2ebef243526e2e269","tid":1755801,"uid":113169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:36:14.000Z","msg":"留名 利申會參加！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128a14e17ce02211b9cf31b3e7dc245134283ee0","tid":1755801,"uid":262340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a19776d1fb6c6dfb8bbe584c6e3bb574668ee1","tid":1755801,"uid":262340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:24:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n我地香港零時論壇嚟近將會搞第一次公民論壇大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkFHkZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkFHkZA.jpg&h=e278c2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><em>點解要搞公民論壇大會？</em></ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地要對抗林鄭政府虛假嘅「和你傾」討論會，創造翻一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">名副其實嘅</span></span></strong>「和你傾」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望香港可以好似1860年代的美國一樣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">隨時隨地</span></span></strong>就可以討論對唔同社會議題，而地點唔再限係維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>呢個論壇有咩用啊？</ins></em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi