 />\n<br />\n呢個活動係好和理非，睇落去好似無咩作用咁<br />\n但係「無大台」要持續落去，就需要每一位香港人學識做功課（包括研究唔同文獻、案例）、學發言，而<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔係再靠代議士做嗮所有嘢</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來獨裁嘅政權最鍾意嘅就係豬</span></span></strong></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以香港人要變得更加聰明、大膽，我地先會有更多本錢and籌碼去對抗任何不公義嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用翻掛係天安門個個死人嘅說話：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">沒有調查就沒有發言權！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持，亦都希望呢個風氣可以蔓延全香港<br />\n多謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:44:01.000Z","msg":"附加翻Telegram<br />\n<br />\n11.30 公民論壇大會 消息頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/thecivilforum1130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fthecivilforum1130&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=a5dbc897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/thecivilforum1130</a>"},{"pid":"9ec3babfeeec319971f0b429894a879002dcad48","tid":1755801,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:47:45.000Z","msg":"怕唔怕變左圍爐大會????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624708ff82c76746a1bfc1d2238d4129a69f559f","tid":1755801,"uid":200464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:48:36.000Z","msg":"會嚟 pish"},{"pid":"bcc4752b04126f1d95a609864b99b6de995c532d","tid":1755801,"uid":11520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T20:17:32.00